00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:54,830
Haló?

477
00:37:54,860 --> 00:37:56,710
<i>Je to Na Mi Rae?</i>

478
00:37:56,720 --> 00:37:57,670
Ano.

479
00:37:57,670 --> 00:37:59,720
<i>Dobrý den, toto je restaurace Provence.</i>

480
00:37:59,730 --> 00:38:03,120
<i>Pod vaším jménem máme uvedenou rezervaci na 24. prosince.</i> 

481
00:38:03,130 --> 00:38:04,590
