482
00:38:04,610 --> 00:38:06,170
<i>Potřebujeme si vaši rezervaci potvrdit.</i>

483
00:38:06,170 --> 00:38:08,600
Ano.

484
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:10,270
Dobře.

485
00:38:10,270 --> 00:38:12,690
Děkuji.

486
00:38:19,610 --> 00:38:23,140
